About
========
Virl-cli is a command line tool to make it more easy to get important information out of Cisco VIRL (Virtual Internet Routing Lab).

Usage
========
After you have created a design and executed the simulation in VM Maestro you can use this tool to get console addresses and ports via command line.

Installation
========
On VIRL host:

apt-get install libjson-perl
git clone https://github.com/tryggvi/virl-cli.git

